 httpd                   x86_64     2.2.3-11.el5_1.3  rhel-x86_64-server-5  1.1 M
 jabberd                 x86_64     2.0s10-3.42.el5  spacewalk         562 k
 mod_python              x86_64     3.2.8-3.1        rhel-x86_64-server-5  260 k
